Package: restbatch
Type: Package
Title: A Simple 'RESTful' Web Service to Schedule R Batch Jobs
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Zhengjia", "Wang", email = "dipterix.wang@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
    )
Description: Starts web services that automatically receive, schedule, and 
    scale up the tasks via the package 'batchtools' as the backend. Provides 
    integration to monitor the submitted tasks in 'RStudio' or 'Shiny' apps.
URL: https://github.com/dipterix/restbatch
BugReports: https://github.com/dipterix/restbatch/issues
